<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="C" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Caparison2" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Caparison,</orth> vb., to cover with a horse-cloth: <emph>c. my horse,</emph> R3<bibl n="shak. wt 5.3.289" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 3, 289</bibl>. Jestingly of human dress: <cit><quote>--ed like a man,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ayl 3.2.205" default="NO" valid="yes">As III, 2, 205</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>--ed like the horse,</quote> <bibl n="shak. shr 3.2.67" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. III, 2, 67</bibl></cit>.
